cat << EOF
 GKrellMLaunch plugin which allows one-click access to frequently used applications from GKrellM.

 Note: requires GKrellM 1.2.2 or higher.

 Offering customisable buttons, GKrellMLaunch allows you to quickly launch a shell, Mozilla etc. with a simple click - all from GKrellM.

     * Unused buttons can be hidden to save screen space.
     * Button labels can be different from command.

EOF
